name: Selfie Nudes in Mirror Concept (Amateurstyle)
description:
Suggested strength: 0.55-0.75 should work with every prompt. The LoRa works with other character LoRas really good in my testings.

Suggested prompt: "<lora:selfspread:0.65> raw photo of woman (selfspread), (taking a selfie in a mirror):1.3" than adding description of woman + usual qualitypromptwords.

The given activationword is "selfspread" most of the trained images was with girls spreading legs in front of mirror so this post produces the best images in my opinion.

By adding the word "mirror" generated picture will show the borders of the mirror, personally like it gives it a more realistic look. For different poses i usually use "kneeling" "legs up" "standin" or "squatting."

This LoRa doesnt give good results with Anime models! And was made and tested with realistic models and a single comic model.

Hope someone can use this. If you like share your results and leave a comment. Have fun.
